document_data.name: Deepbeak
document_data.mainbody: '''Deepbeak''' was a subterranean [[owlbear]] that lived beneath [[Myth Drannor]] in the late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].{{DDO-MoMDtime}}
document_data.History: The beast dwelled within the catacombs beneath [[Ildrannath's Tower]], deep below the city.
